{"tid":1609471,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"荃灣一役有感而發","createTime":"2019-10-01T14:39:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T16:23:39.000Z","uid":307195,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3d6901fb01b267bf01df956ba439f7008dde3791","tid":1609471,"uid":307195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14:39:11.000Z","msg":"發你老母<br />\n手足中槍 差啲中心臟 <br />\n我知好多人都好撚嬲 <br />\n我求下大家記住呢班黑警一直以黎既所作所為<br />\n唔好比時間沖淡你哋嘅憤怒<br />\n一世都唔好原諒呢班黑警 <br />\n「警察」呢個職業喺香港世世代代都要人見人憎<br />\n「香港警察」一世都係過街老鼠<br />\n每次都要犧牲手足去換取輿論壓力<br />\n真係好撚好撚心痛<br />\n我懇請咁多位唔好放棄<br />\n呢場仗仲未打完<br />\n對準政權 清算黑警<br />\n堅持落去 香港人"},{"pid":"3c76dddcfafe92e945cc98a59d85c3206fe84143","tid":1609471,"uid":30113,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14:40:45.000Z","msg":"我要黑警成世都仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49b194faceffc5a12d23778b64939122a21c5964","tid":1609471,"uid":161436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:43:12.000Z","msg":"黑警做嘅每一件事 呢世都唔會忘記"},{"pid":"596906229aaae30730a934a49b9161a0d4b17d76","tid":1609471,"uid":317944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:23:39.000Z","msg":"我會用我既一生去憎佢哋"}]}